what is an events : 
event is an action that happens in the browser . 
examples : clicking a button , moving mouse , pressing keys ,submitting form and loading a page.
java script can detects these events and respond to them 

types of events : there are 3 types of events as : mouse event , keyboard event and browser event . 
mouse event : click , dblclick , mouse hover , mouse out.
keyboard events : keydown and keyup
browser events : load , resize and scroll

